comments: Lee (GSW) gives Simons (POR) room to land on the jump shot attempt as the two make slight contact.
Whiteside (POR) cleanly blocks Lee's (GSW) shot attempt, any additional contact to his body is deemed incidental.
Lee (GSW) makes marginal contact to the arm of Trent Jr. (POR) after the release that does not affect his jump shot or follow through.
Paschall (GSW) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Paschall (GSW) briefly grasp the arm of Anthony (POR) on his drive, but does not disrupt Anthony's ability to defend.
Anthony (POR) makes slight contact to the arm of Paschall (GSW) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Whiteside (POR) and Burks (GSW) make marginal contact with one another after the pick.

Cauley-Stein (GSW) places a resting hand on Lillard's (POR) body while defending the drive to the basket and shot attempt. The contact does not restrict Lillard's SQBR while Cauley-Stein cleanly blocks the lay up attempt.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) is firming up and makes slight lower body contact with Lillard (POR) during the pick.
Replay review of the foul called on Trent Jr. (POR)  pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Burks (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Lillard (POR).
Lillard (POR) makes contact to the body of Russell (GSW) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Whiteside (POR) and Cauley-Stein (GSW) briefly engage and disengage with one another during the rebound.
Whiteside (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Burks (GSW). No one touches Lee (GSW) while he makes contact with Burks on the shot.
Burks (GSW) and Lillard (POR) mutually engage with one another during the pick.
Lee (GSW) does not give Simons (POR) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
Trent Jr. (POR) makes contact to the body of Burks (GSW) on the drive.
Lillard (POR) places a resting hand on Lee's (GSW) body during the rebound.
Trent Jr. (POR) gives Paschall (GSW) room to land on the jump shot attempt. The pair make contact after Paschall extends his legs unnaturally.
Burks (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Lillard (POR). After the pick, Whiteside (POR) makes contact with Lillard's body on the shot.
Paschall (GSW) maintains a legal gather and steps as he drives to the basket.
Whiteside (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Paschall (GSW) and cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Paschall (GSW) delivers contact to the lower body of Whiteside (POR) after he leads with his knee on the shot attempt.
Trent Jr. (POR) seeks out the contact unnaturally with Cauley-Stein (GSW) on the play at the basket and delivers contact to his head.

After the inbound pass, Hezonja (POR) makes brief hot stove contact to the body of Burks (GSW) as the play develops. As Burks beings his shooting motion, Hezonja retreats his hand into a legal position.
Burks (GSW) makes contact to the body of Lillard (POR) during his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Hezonja (POR) during the pick.
Burks (GSW) dislodges Whiteside (POR) from his position during the rebound.
Lee (GSW) makes contact to the arm of Lillard (POR) on the rebound.
Chriss (GSW) is firmed up and makes slight contact with Hezonja (POR) during the screen.
